        </header>

        <div class="main-grid">
            
            <div class="left-col">
                <div class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Professional Profile</div>
                <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    Detail-oriented Informatics Engineering student specializing in <b>System Administration</b> and <b>Backend Development</b>. 
                    Experienced in building internal tools for operational efficiency and managing Linux-based infrastructure. 
                    Seeking to leverage skills in PHP, Linux, and Network Management in a challenging professional environment.
                </p>

                <div class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Experience</div>
                
                <div class="exp-item">
                    <h4>IT Support Intern</h4>
                    <div class="exp-company">PT. Saraswanti Indoland Development Tbk</div>
                    <span class="exp-date">Sep 2024 - Jan 2025</span>
                    <ul class="exp-list">
                        <li>Engineered a custom web application to digitize and streamline internal data entry, reducing manual processing time.</li>
                        <li>Orchestrated data tabulation and backup strategies to ensure 100% data availability for project stakeholders.</li>
                        <li>Provided critical technical support and network monitoring during high-priority corporate events.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Education</div>
                <div class="exp-item" style="border: none; padding-bottom: 0;">
                    <h4>Diploma of Informatics Engineering</h4>
